snippet.title: Omega Quintet -- Teaser Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
The world is ending and humanity’s only hope is a singing idol group! In this hybrid RPG/idol simulation, five idols wield Sound Weapons against the dark forces of the world. Build up an arsenal of attacks, get the crowd’s pulse racing with extraordinary skills, and then get them on their feet with your own choreographed idol performance!
